      "locked": false,
      "text": "+-------------------------------------- Table (整张数据表) ----------------------------------\n-------------------------+\n| [Row Group 0] | [Row Group 1] | [Row Group 2] | ... | [Row Group N]  (按行切\n分的物理存储单元，每单元含连续行数据)                     |\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n-------------------------------------------+\n        │                  │                  │                   │\n        ▼                  ▼                  ▼                   ▼\n+------------------- Row Group 0 --------------------+  +------------------- Row Group\n1 --------------------+\n| [Column 0 Data] | [Column 1 Data] | [Column 2 Data] |  | [Column 0 Data] |\n[Column 1 Data] | [Column 2 Data] |\n| (行1~1500的ID列) | (行1~1500数值列) | (行1~1500字符串列) |  | (行1501~3300ID\n列)| (行1501~3300数值列)| (行1501~3300字符串列)|\n+----------------------------------------------------+  +---------------------------------------\n-------------+\n        │                  │                  │\n        ▼                  ▼                  ▼\n+------------- Column 0 Data -------------+  +------------- Column 1 Data -------------\n+\n| [Seg 0] | [Seg 1] | [Seg 2] | ... | [Seg M] |  | [Seg 0] | [Seg 1] | [Seg 2] | ... |\n[Seg M] |\n| (ID段1) | (ID段2) | (ID段3) |     | (ID段M) |  | (数值段1)| (数值段2)| (数值段3)|\n| (数值段M)|\n+-----------------------------------------+  +-----------------------------------------+",
